relevant_findings.description: Document relates to Cuban revolutionary activities, mentioning Ernesto Guevara's military movements
relevant_findings.direct_quote: ERNESTO GUEVARA HAS MOVED WESTWARD. HIS EXACT LOCATION NOT KNOWN BUT 165 MEN THOUGHT TO BE UNDER HIS COMMAND ARE CAMPED NEAR MANACAS IN WEST LAS VILLAS
relevant_findings.significance: Provides context of Cuban revolutionary activities around 1958, but no direct connection to JFK assassination
